<item>
            <title>[LU-15459] close(2) fails with EIO on enosp</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15459</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When write switches to sync commit async due lack of disk space async error codes remain set to -28. That causes close(2) to fail&#160; as ll_flush() catches the async errors and returns -EIO.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The async errors should be catched and cleared after call to vvp_io_commit_sync() to prevent ll_flush() and close(2) from failing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
